### List Media (PosMediaMaster search)
GET http://localhost:4200/mediaMaster?orgIds=9f4f98d7-ffcf-4af4-89b3-1858b26c79de&isAppluUnderOrg=false&targetDate=2025-01-01&keyWord=&mediaSearchType=ALL

### List Media for specific org and date, only VALID
GET http://localhost:4200/mediaMaster?orgIds={{ORG_ID}}&isAppluUnderOrg=false&targetDate=2025-01-01&keyWord=&mediaSearchType=VALID

### Get Media Detail (for edit button)
GET http://localhost:4200/mediaMaster/detail?mediaId={{MEDIA_ID}}&targetDate=2025-01-01&mediaSearchType=VALID

### Create new Media
POST http://localhost:4200/mediaMaster?applyDate=2025-01-01&applyStartDate=2025-01-01&mediaId=&mediaSearchType=VALID&invalidChangeFlag=0
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dispOrder": 10,
  "mediaCode": "WEB_AD",
  "mediaName": "Web Advertising",
  "mediaCategory": 1,
  "effective": true,
  "orgIds": [
    "9f4f98d7-ffcf-4af4-89b3-1858b26c79de"
    // "{{ORG_ID_2}}"
  ]
}

### Update existing Media (change name/order/effective/orgs)
POST http://localhost:4200/mediaMaster?applyDate=2025-11-30&applyStartDate=2025-11-30&mediaId=c40d5902-8beb-4830-9dde-f6c3ac8cc189&mediaSearchType=VALID&invalidChangeFlag=1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dispOrder": 11,
  "mediaCode": "WEB_AD",
  "mediaName": "Web Advertising Updated 2",
  "mediaCategory": 1,
  "effective": false,
  "orgIds": [
    "9f4f98d7-ffcf-4af4-89b3-1858b26c79de"
  ]
}

### Notes
# - mediaCode should be unique across medias.
# - mediaCategory must match numeric values used in MEDIA_CATEGORY_GROUP on FE.
# - targetDate / applyDate / applyStartDate are YYYY-MM-DD.
# - orgIds should be UUIDs of org records.
# - invalidChangeFlag is currently accepted but not deeply interpreted; 0/1/2 are all allowed.

